des:
Wellness Radio 1570 broadcasts from the Twin Cities Minneapolis region. The station is currently the only of its kind dedicating its entire format to health and wellness programming. Wellness radio 1570 features shows like, Dr. Asa On Call weekdays from noon to 3pm along with great local programming dedicated to helping listeners live longer and healthier lives.
